itunes:title: Listen to this if you are in a slump
title: Listen to this if you are in a slump
itunes:author: Joey Kidney
itunes:summary:
Slumps are literally the worst. We feel stuck, alone, and weak. Well I am here with my 6 step plan to not fix your slump, but hopefully help you to try to fix it yourself.
